1. create bucket after login into amazon aws console
2. bucket name should be unique in that region
3. open up IAM in new tab, click on policies
4. Click on create policy and select S3 service and allow all the actions, 
 	for resources - click on specific and then to bucket (add ARN) and provide your bucket name 
 			and for object (add bucket name inside bucket and add any for object)
 	ARN - identifier for specific bucket we created
5. Give policy name and create the policy
6. Create programmable access key


After uploading is done, we have to change some AWS S3 bucket policy to access the uploaded file
1. Go to S3 dashboard and inside bucket policy and generate policy using policy generator
2. Select 'GetObject' action and principal as * and insert ARN as suggested